title: Projected Business Formations within 8 Quarters for Vermont (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFPBF8QTOTALNSAVT (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFPBF8QTOTALNSAVT) for an alternative.

The projected number of employer businesses that originate from Business Applications (BA) within eight quarters from the quarter of application, similar to https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PBF4QNSAVT. The projected business formation series cover the period for which the actual business formations are not yet available.
